<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>808</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>wǒ men tóng yǒu yī gè jiā 迦南808</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men tóng yǒu yī gè jiā, tóng yǒu yī gè jiā. tóng yǒu yī gè shǐ mìng, fàng yě fàng bù xià.
 dào yuǎn fāng dào tiān yá, bǎ zhǔ ài bō sā. yīn wèi yé sū kuài huí lái le.
 qīn rén nǎ, wǒ men lù guò nǐ de jiā, xīn lǐ zhǐ yǒu yī jù huà. bù guǎn
 dào lù yǒu duō jiān nán, yī dìng yào gēn zhe tā. wǒ men de qīn rén dōu bǎ nǐ qiān guà.</lyrics>
</song>